# Environment Configuration Template
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual values
# NEVER commit .env to version control!

# ====================================================================
# Cloudflare Worker Environment Variables (set via Cloudflare Dashboard)
# ====================================================================
# These are NOT used by the frontend. They must be set in your
# Cloudflare Worker environment variables or .dev.vars file.
#
# DS_KEY — DeepSeek API Key (get from: https://platform.deepseek.com/api-keys)
# ALLOWED_ORIGIN — Your domain, e.g. https://mpalomaresdigitalsolutions.site
# TURNSTILE_SECRET — Cloudflare Turnstile secret key
#
# See: workers/chat-proxy.js and wrangler.toml

# ====================================================================
# Frontend Configuration (index.html only)
# ====================================================================
# Set PROXY_URL in index.html to your deployed Cloudflare Worker URL.
# Example PROXY_URL = 'https://chat-proxy.your-subdomain.workers.dev'
#
# SHEET_URL — Google Apps Script endpoint for saving contact form data.
# This is obfuscated in index.html and is optional.

# Instructions:
# 1. Deploy the Cloudflare Worker (see workers/chat-proxy.js)
# 2. Set DS_KEY and ALLOWED_ORIGIN in the Cloudflare Worker dashboard
# 3. Set PROXY_URL in index.html to your worker URL
# 4. Never share your DS_KEY or .env file
